Provides: coding-agent-ui
Description: Way of Pi — Pi Coding Agent desktop shell

 Way of Pi is a friendly wrapper around the Pi Coding Agent, providing
 a full desktop application for interacting with an AI coding assistant.
 
 Features include:
 - Full desktop UI with file explorer, chat, and code editor
 - Multiple agent teams and customizable extensions
 - Support for various AI models (Ollama, OpenRouter, etc.)
 - Optional Honcho memory integration for cross-session context

 This is not a pre-compiled binary. You must install build dependencies
 (bun, npm, git) before use.
